<img src="https://i0.wp.com/notjustok.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Vibe-Art-Cover.jpg?ssl=1" alt="Avit - Vibe (Prod. Kuvie)" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Vibe artwork Ghanaian singer and songwriter Avit presents his debut single, simply titled "Vibe". "Vibe" is a mellow, mid-tempo afrobeats song, where Avit philosophizes on the pressures of life and the desire to achieve, but also the need to let go and unwind when need be. "Vibe" was produced by talented Ghanaian producer Kuvie, producer of hit songs by La Meme Gang, Darkovibes, Pappy Kojo, A.I, and more. Check out the joint below, and let us know what you think in the comments! Enjoy! See also: Kuvie ft. B4Bonah & RJZ – Energy Connect with Avit on social media via Twitter @official_avit GET MORE: Avit Songs and Videos HERE Listen to the MP3 and watch the video; what are your thoughts about this new song, "Vibe"? Leave your comment below! The post Avit – Vibe (Prod. Kuvie) appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Original Article Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.